OL,7,FA schizophrenic man who killed three
OL,8,Fpensioners in Devon cannot sue
OL,9,Fauthorities over allegations he faced
OL,10,Fnegligent treatment before the
OL,11,Fattacks, the Supreme Court has ruled.
OL,13,FIn 2019, Alexander Lewis-Ranwell was
OL,14,Ffound not guilty by reason of insanity
OL,15,Fof the murders of Anthony Payne, 80,
OL,16,Fand 84-year-old twins Dick and Roger
OL,17,FCarter in February that year, with a
OL,18,Fjudge giving him a hospital order with
OL,19,Frestrictions.
