OL,3,CSchizophrenic man who killed three
OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe killings in Exeter came just hours
OL,8,Fafter Lewis-Ranwell had been released
OL,9,Ffrom custody for attacking an elderly
OL,10,Ffarmer with a saw.
OL,12,FIn 2020, Lewis-Ranwell, who is now 34,
OL,13,Fsued Devon and Cornwall Police, G4S
OL,14,FHealth Services (UK), Devon
OL,15,FPartnership NHS Trust and Devon County
OL,16,FCouncil, claiming all four were
OL,17,Fnegligent in their treatment of him by
OL,18,Ffailing to provide adequate care and
OL,19,Freleasing him back into the community
OL,20,Fbefore the attacks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
