OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, five Supreme Court
OL,8,Fjustices unanimously ruled that Lewis-
OL,9,FRanwell was barred from suing the
OL,10,Fauthorities for damages, finding that
OL,11,Fthe "denial of the claim would not be
OL,12,Fa disproportionate response" to his
OL,13,Fillegality.
OL,15,FIn a ruling backed by Lord Reed, Lady
OL,16,FRose and Lady Simler, Lords Hodge and
OL,17,FLloyd-Jones said that the killings
OL,18,Fwere "unlawful conduct for the
OL,19,Fpurposes of engaging the illegality
OL,20,Fdefence".
OL,26,@sD@EOUtD@\O]zD@FOU|D@HO]
