OL,3,CSchizophrenic man who killed three
OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThey said: "Killing another human
OL,8,Fbeing without lawful justification
OL,9,Fbreaches a fundamental moral rule in
OL,10,Four society, you shall not kill.
OL,12,F"This is so even when the person who
OL,13,Fhas killed bears no criminal
OL,14,Fresponsibility for his actions."
OL,16,FThey continued: "His lawful detention,
OL,17,Fwhich the court has authorised by the
OL,18,Fhospital order and restriction order,
OL,19,Fis the consequence of those actions."
