OL,3,CSchizophrenic man who killed three
OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe justices said that Lewis-Ranwell
OL,8,Fwas diagnosed with schizophrenia in
OL,9,Fhis mid-20s.
OL,11,FHe was arrested on 8 February 2019 on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of burglary at a farm in
OL,13,FBarnstaple, and was bailed the next
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FLater that day, he was arrested for
OL,17,Fcausing grievous bodily harm to an
OL,18,Felderly man and was bailed again on 10
OL,19,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
