OL,3,CSchizophrenic man who killed three
OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe justices continued that during
OL,8,Fboth periods in custody, Lewis-Ranwell
OL,9,Fbehaved "violently and erratically and
OL,10,Fwas apparently mentally very unwell".
OL,12,FHe was seen by G4S and NHS staff, and
OL,13,Fdespite a face-to-face mental health
OL,14,Fassessment being discussed, it was not
OL,15,Farranged.
OL,17,FLewis-Ranwell killed the three men
OL,18,Fwhile on bail for a second time,
OL,19,Fbefore his arrest on 11 February.
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@dO]
