OL,3,CSchizophrenic man who killed three
OL,4,Cpensioners cannot sue authorities for
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FBut the Supreme Court disagreed, with
OL,8,FLords Hodge and Lloyd-Jones stating
OL,9,Fthe Court of Appeal "places too much
OL,10,Fweight on the absence of moral
OL,11,Fculpability".
OL,13,FThe inquests of Mr Payne, Dick Carter
OL,14,Fand Roger Carter are yet to take
OL,15,Fplace, having been postponed earlier
OL,16,Fthis month.
